      .row
        .box
          .col-lg-12
            %hr
              %h2.intro-text.text-center
                Beautiful boxes
                %strong to showcase your content
              %hr
                %p Use as many boxes as you like, and put anything you want in them! They are great for just about anything, the sky's the limit!
